{
  "description": "A vibrant and dramatic sunset over a hilly landscape and body of water. The sky is dominated by fiery red and orange hues, with wispy, streaky clouds creating a textured and dynamic pattern. The clouds are most intense in color closest to the horizon, gradually fading to deeper blues and purples higher in the sky. Below the horizon line, a dark silhouette of hills and a distant city skyline are visible. The horizon glows with a warm orange light, reflecting on the water's surface. Some greenery is visible in the very foreground.",
